h3. Purpose

To give the sanity checker an entity to perform checks upon.

h3. Example

{code}
SanityChecker checker = new SanityChecker()

checker.check('Item 1', 1)
checker.check('Item 2', 2, 'Sample Input')
{code}

h3. @IllegalArgumentException@

@check@ throws an @IllegalArgumentException@ if the *name* parameter is
@null@ or an empty @String@ ("").
